{"tid":1361732,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到有答案] 林鄭係咪畀人挾持緊?","createTime":"2019-07-24T16:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T09:36:39.000Z","uid":266107,"like":72,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"aa881daa4767603ffd05d5a72a3b2e1f2fa86f93","tid":1361732,"uid":266107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:20:15.000Z","msg":"簡單到 &quot;撤回&quot; 都講唔出? 個個禮拜睇住事情情不斷惡化， 但竟然神穩。<br />\n但係依家衰嘢佢要食曬。 其實一個正常人都會明哲保身。<br />\n如果正正常常，其實可以企喺香港人嗰邊， 講返正常的話，話曬係港人治港。<br />\n星期一 所有官員個死狗樣， 行會除咗葉劉個個都咁頹廢， 湯家驊冇出現。 個個死狗樣，好似畀人挾持唔可以跳船。<br />\n<br />\n你估林鄭係咪畀人挾持? 最多都係挾持佢兩仔同埋老公， 其實未必需要為咗三個人而騎劫成個香港。<br />\n<br />\n你哋點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推到有答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100b4eab90995ad8844c1f1e76144eb747d7cf46","tid":1361732,"uid":7843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"依個問題我都開過post問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63b3d0e29bfa1728ea8b1a852d522941bdfb1d7","tid":1361732,"uid":266107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:22:06.000Z","msg":"所以連登仔, 所有高人有冇見解?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c0326c9a207af3d1946e45b19105b6d3f63e88","tid":1361732,"uid":266107,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:22:47.000Z","msg":"推到有答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59a15861ad23aa6ee251b419fd8781c65a6ef3e","tid":1361732,"uid":266107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59eda50c1505aab29cdad1a6dbba38d65edace6f","tid":1361732,"uid":266107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/